566
00:26:13,630 --> 00:26:15,070
I am.

567
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:17,030
But our budget for this

568
00:26:17,030 --> 00:26:18,110
is 15,000.

569
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:18,980
