again and again,

573
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:24,180
it'll create a snowball effect.

574
00:26:24,180 --> 00:26:25,330
Things will get uncontrollable.

575
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:27,740
Do you understand, you dummy?

576
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:30,740
I don't know why you are even here.

577
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:33,180
Yes.

578
00:26:33,940 --> 00:26:34,870
You are right.

579
00:26:35,550 --> 00:26:36,630
You are always right.

580
00:26:37,740 --> 00:26:38,900
What should we do now?

581
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:41,140
We have to compare the prices.

582
00:26:56,140 --> 00:26:57,030
What are you doing?

583
00:26:57,790 --> 00:26:59,180
You'll be the brain

584
00:26:59,460 --> 00:27:00,180
and I

585
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:01,550
will be the brawn.

586
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:03,420
Let's go.

587
00:27:06,170 --> 00:27:08,810
