589
00:27:13,370 --> 00:27:15,290
♪Your hand♪

590
00:27:16,090 --> 00:27:19,490
♪Hold me into warm world♪

591
00:27:20,450 --> 00:27:22,650
♪That I can build a dream♪

592
00:27:22,650 --> 00:27:26,970
♪Hope this comes true♪

593
00:27:28,010 --> 00:27:30,210
♪You♪

594
00:27:30,530 --> 00:27:34,810
♪You know it's you♪

595
00:27:34,810 --> 00:27:37,890
♪All I need is you♪

596
00:27:38,570 --> 00:27:42,530
♪All I want is you♪

597
00:27:42,610 --> 00:27:43,570
♪You♪

598
00:27:44,810 --> 00:27:47,330
♪You know only you♪

599
00:27:49,250 --> 00:27:51,650
♪All I love is you♪

600
00:27:52,810 --> 00:27:55,010
♪And no one can replace you♪

601
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:56,660
Look at this. This is more scratch-proof

602
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:57,700
and durable.

603
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:59,660
