that are a little bit warmer?

604
00:27:59,660 --> 00:28:00,630
A little bit warmer.

605
00:28:00,740 --> 00:28:01,550
Let me take a look.

606
00:28:02,270 --> 00:28:04,030
What about this? Do you like this?

607
00:28:04,270 --> 00:28:05,390
I think this will do.

608
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,140
What about the price?

609
00:28:07,490 --> 00:28:08,690
It'll be 360 per square meter.

610
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:10,030
What do you think?

611
00:28:11,110 --> 00:28:11,830
Let me think.

612
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:12,660
Honey.

613
00:28:13,490 --> 00:28:15,110
I'm getting hungry
from all the shopping.

614
00:28:15,700 --> 00:28:16,980
Can you give me five yuan

615
00:28:17,250 --> 00:28:18,420
so that I can buy some food?

616
00:28:26,790 --> 00:28:27,590
Sure.

617
00:28:30,170 --> 00:28:35,650
(Wood Veneers, Ecological Boards,
Decorative Panels)

618
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:42,230
I never thought that the potatoes here
would taste so good.

619
00:28:42,420 --> 00:28:43,220
Honey.

620
00:28:43,390 --> 00:28:44,030
Mr. Lu.

621
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:46,180
We are done with shopping now.

622
00:28:46,550 --> 00:28:48,030
Stop taking advantage of me.

623
00:28:50,940 --> 00:28:53,550
I just want to say
that these potatoes taste good.

624
00:28:54,220 --> 00:28:54,830
Ms.

625
00:28:55,830 --> 00:28:56,460
Shen.

626
00:28:57,740 --> 00:29:00,310
Besides, you can't be sure
who's taking advantage of who.

627
00:29:00,740 --> 00:29:03,180
You looked quite happy too just now.

628
00:29:04,550 --> 00:29:07,500
I was happy because
I got to save some money.

629
00:29:07,870 --> 00:29:09,420
Not because I called you...

630
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:11,940
honey.

631
00:29:17,220 --> 00:29:18,420
Do you still remember

632
00:29:19,140 --> 00:29:20,140
you told me last time

633
00:29:20,140 --> 00:29:22,110
that I was different
from what you remembered?

634
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:23,390
Yes.

635
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:25,590
You gave me a summary.

636
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:27,920
You said that your brain
had a second development period.

637
00:29:29,660 --> 00:29:30,630
I think

638
00:29:31,590 --> 00:29:33,460
you are different
from what I remember too.

639
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:44,030
What was I like

640
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:46,350
in your memory?

641
00:30:38,630 --> 00:30:39,740
Why do you keep quiet?

642
00:30:40,980 --> 00:30:44,350
Have you forgotten
what I was like in the past?

643
00:30:47,590 --> 00:30:50,550
I tried so hard to recall just now.

644
00:30:52,310 --> 00:30:53,740
But I couldn't.

645
00:30:54,350 --> 00:30:55,920
Maybe because
you weren't that important.

646
00:30:56,940 --> 00:30:57,630
I forgot.

647
00:30:58,360 --> 00:30:59,140
I forgot everything.

648
00:31:02,700 --> 00:31:04,940
Being dumb and having a bad memory.

649
00:31:05,500 --> 00:31:07,310
As expected of you, Lu Xingyan.

650
00:31:07,940 --> 00:31:08,940
You still haven't changed

651
00:31:09,740 --> 00:31:10,940
after so many years.

652
00:31:11,350 --> 00:31:12,550
When have you come up

653
00:31:12,550 --> 00:31:13,740
with such a false conclusion?

654
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:16,500
When I was tutoring you back then,

655
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:19,620
you couldn't remember even after
I taught you the same question 10 times.

656
00:31:19,630 --> 00:31:21,700
In the end, even I couldn't remember.

657
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:23,650
I couldn't even remember if I had
taught you about something or not.

658
00:31:29,390 --> 00:31:31,410
Although I was scolded
by Ms. Shen every day back then,

659
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:34,220
it was quite a happy time
when I think about it now.

660
00:31:35,560 --> 00:31:37,030
Actually, it would be nice if I could

661
00:31:38,870 --> 00:31:39,940
turn back time.

662
00:31:42,870 --> 00:31:45,140
At that time, we had no worries in life.

663
00:31:45,460 --> 00:31:46,830
It was the happiest moment

664
00:31:46,830 --> 00:31:48,390
in our lives.

665
00:31:50,830 --> 00:31:52,940
If only we couldn't return to the past.

666
00:31:55,740 --> 00:31:56,460
Shen Xingruo.

667
00:32:01,630 --> 00:32:02,900
Should we...

668
00:32:19,140 --> 00:32:19,940
Lu Xingyan.

669
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,550
What are you trying to say?

670
00:32:24,630 --> 00:32:25,500
Should we...

