674
00:32:46,730 --> 00:32:48,850
(Among the three pairs,
which one do you think will fail?)

675
00:32:48,850 --> 00:32:50,050
Who asked this question?

676
00:32:50,050 --> 00:32:50,970
It's tough.

677
00:32:52,030 --> 00:32:53,970
It's for the show.
We have to make it interesting

678
00:32:53,970 --> 00:32:55,630
by asking the guests
to comment on each other.

679
00:32:59,210 --> 00:33:00,170
Lu Xingyan.

680
00:33:00,170 --> 00:33:01,930
I think Lu Xingyan will fail.

681
00:33:02,370 --> 00:33:03,170
Why?

682
00:33:04,610 --> 00:33:07,210
Because Lu Xingyan
doesn't deserve Shen Xingruo.

683
00:33:07,650 --> 00:33:09,850
He has always forced his mindset

684
00:33:09,850 --> 00:33:11,290
on Xingruo.

685
00:33:11,610 --> 00:33:13,770
He doesn't know what Xingruo wanted.

686
00:33:15,090 --> 00:33:17,490
Back then, after they broke up,

687
00:33:17,490 --> 00:33:19,850
Xingruo called him
to reconcile with him.

688
00:33:19,850 --> 00:33:22,810
But he refused to pick up her call, twice.

689
00:33:26,730 --> 00:33:28,410
I don't think anyone will fail.

690
00:33:28,410 --> 00:33:29,930
But I think I know which one
will be the most successful one.

691
00:33:30,570 --> 00:33:32,490
Are you talking about yourself?

692
00:33:34,130 --> 00:33:35,090
How do you know?

693
00:33:36,390 --> 00:33:38,030
Do you think
that I'll be successful too?

